  "prompt": "Can I deposit cash without cheque in SBI?",
  "response": "Yes, you can deposit cash without a cheque at the State Bank of India (SBI). Here are a few methods you can use:\n\n1. **Cash Deposit Machine (CDM):** Many SBI branches have Cash Deposit Machines where you can deposit cash directly into your account without the need for a bank slip or cheque.\n\n2. **Bank Branch:** You can visit an SBI branch and deposit cash directly at the counter. You will usually need to fill out a cash deposit slip and present it along with the cash to the teller.\n\n3. **Automated Teller Machines (ATMs):** Some SBI ATMs are equipped with cash deposit facilities. You can deposit cash directly into your account through these ATMs.\n\nMake sure to check with your local SBI branch for the specific procedures and available facilities, as they may vary.",
